
pre_vent

prevent = 防止 / 阻止 / 讓…不發生

prevent the fire from spreading.
prevent any mistakes.
prevent a major accident
prevent the problem from getting worse.





I wash my hands to prevent sickness.
The mask can prevent germs from spreading.
He ran fast to prevent being late.
We must prevent accidents at work.
Good planning can prevent problems.



⚠️ 小提醒
prevent = 阻止某事發生
不同於 stop（stop 可以中途阻止，也可完全停止）
prevent 更偏向 事前預防


❗ 常見搭配
prevent + 人 / 物 + from + V-ing
